00:20:18.039 --> 00:20:20.090
The Netflix Book Club!

00:20:20.090 --> 00:20:22.390
Have you heard of it?

00:20:22.390 --> 00:20:31.330
This lady, Uzo Aduba, analyses and interviews
the author for every book that has been made

00:20:31.330 --> 00:20:35.380
